      },
      "parameters": [],
      "title": "homogeneous_2d_passivation",
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "Champion active-area efficiency of 25.61% for 0.14 cm2 small devices using the DABr/FABr homogeneous 2D passivation strategy with antisolvent-free processing",
